    {
      "id": "PopularPost306947",
      "post_content": "Wouldn't giving your ally in a multiplayer game the vow be better than giving them Ruhan himself? That way you can still sacrifice Ruhan if you have any effects that require it, and they can't sacrifice it to their cards if they turn against you. It also allows you to use enchantment bounce or removal on the vow to let Ruhan hit them when you are no longer allies and prevents them from doing that to you. ",
      "posted_by": "EvilDarkVoid",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost306947\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Wouldn't giving your ally in a multiplayer game the vow be better than giving them Ruhan himself? That way you can still sacrifice Ruhan if you have any effects that require it, and they can't sacrifice it to their cards if they turn against you. It also allows you to use enchantment bounce or removal on the vow to let Ruhan hit them when you are no longer allies and prevents them from doing that to you. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '306947'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy95215\">EvilDarkVoid</span>\r\n                                (4/3/2013 10:17:22 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../