    {
      "id": "PopularPost228518",
      "post_content": "Interestingly, Ruhan here is from the same tribe of giants seen in Future Sight ([Fomori Nomad](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fomori Nomad)). [The Mimeoplasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Mimeoplasm) also apparently roams Muraganda, a land referenced in Future Sight as well ([Muraganda Petroglyphs](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Muraganda Petroglyphs)). This leads me to believe that the Fomori and Muraganda are on the same plane, and will be in the same set. I may very well be wrong though, we'll have to see what the future holds.",
      "posted_by": "Sutebe",
